,"links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/4974"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Musculoskeletal Presentations","synonyms":null,"description":null,"position":null,"createdAt":"2024-10-17T23:22:36+10:30","updatedAt":"2024-10-17T23:22:36+10:30"},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"22"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"type":"tags","id":"11633","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/11633"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Musculoskeletal (MSK)","synonyms":null,"description":null,"position":19,"createdAt":"2025-02-28T03:40:40+10:30","updatedAt":"2025-02-28T03:40:40+10:30"},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"15"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"type":"contributions","id":"6051","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/contributions/6051"},"attributes":{"createdAt":"2022-12-03T11:53:39+10:30","finalizedAt":"2023-01-05T17:58:56+10:30","userDetails":{"name":"Kayla Nathin","title":"","isExpert":false,"position":"Intern","training":"Intern","credentials":"MBBS","institutionOther":"Lyell McEwin Hospital"},"instructions":"\u003Cp\u003EBuild into the stem the various dynamics that are mentioned in the options. Perhaps make the reference to leg weakness rather more subtle. You could say that she was recently in hospital for a flare up of her COPD and had a course of steroids. Also that she has a history of IV drug abuse in her youth. Need a rather more aggressive cancer for option A - but not one that commonly metastasises to bone. Will need another option for E, if we build steroids into C. The question could be along the lines of \u0027Which one of the following is most suggestive of the need for further assessment?\u0027\u003C/p\u003E","lastViewedAt":"2023-03-05T22:42:20+10:30","lastActivityAt":"2023-01-05T12:43:37+10:30","readAt":"2023-01-05T12:43:37+10:30","price":15,"paidAt":"2023-01-11T10:24:55+10:30","toCharity":false,"fromWorklist":true,"onWorklist":false,"isPr